Pursuer Evader Game
-------------------

This directory should be used internally.
It is not part of Tenet distribution software.

It is a Tenet application that depends on the robotics library. 

Requirements
------------
Need library lplayer from software player disponible at 
http://playerstage.sourceforge.net/


To run
------
-Turn robot Pioneer on
-Enable it to move motors (paly white button)
-Execute player client at robot
-Execute particle filter (at this subdirectory pf_loc)
-File rthTopology6.in represents the topology map.
-Execute ./PEG rthTopology6.in -r
-For usage, type ./PEG -anything
